Trinity Empire would like to thank everyone who made this APP possible. Many Thanks to Jokebed Boyer for reviewing every single book, chapter, verse on the BIB LA. Without her strenuous work, this would not have been possible.Thanks goes out to Stephanie Boyer for providing us with the 'vèsè jounen an', the Lord will recompense you for your hard and dedicated work. Thanks also go out to Nathalie Pierre, Erika Jean-Baptiste, for their unfiltered honest feedback which resulted in a much better APP.

Thank you everyone for dowloading the BIB LA App. We, at Trinity Empire, pray that this Bible can be a source of encouragement.
